# Invite links: /join/<game-id> open the app on a device that has Jottly (via the
# apple-app-site-association file); on everything else they fall through to this landing page.
# Target the extensionless /invite (not /invite.html) so Cloudflare's automatic .html stripping
# can't bounce the rewrite through a 307 - this serves the page in place at the original URL.
/join/*  /invite  200
/join    /invite  200

# Daily challenge: on a device with Jottly the /daily universal link opens the app straight into the
# daily (via the apple-app-site-association file). Everyone else gets daily.html - a DIRECT 200 page
# (not a redirect) so shared /daily links render a rich Messages/OG preview card like /join does; a
# 302 to home genericized or dropped the card. Cloudflare serves daily.html at /daily via clean URLs.
